        <section style="background-image: url('<%= asset_path("community.png") %>');" class="block bg-cover bg-center w-full relative" id="about">
          <div class="text-white max-w-screen-xl mx-auto">
            <h3 class="font-Outfit font-normal text-base text-center p-5">HOW WE DO THAT</h3>
            <h3 class="font-Outfit font-bold text-2xl mt-3 text-center">HOW WE GET RESULTS THAT LAST</h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:flex md:justify-center gap-4 p-6 font-Outfit text-white overflow-x-auto w-full">
              <%= render partial: 'shared/card', locals: { svg_icon_path: 'gift.svg', title: 'GIVE A DONATION', description: 'Support our cause with your treasures in either funding, materials or alms', action_text: 'DONATE', variant_class: 'h-72', image_container_class: '', text_alignment_class: '', action_text_class: '' } %>
              <%= render partial: 'shared/card', locals: { svg_icon_path: 'accessible.svg', title: 'VOLUNTEER NOW', description: 'Take time to make impact as you serve humanity together', action_text: 'JOIN IN', variant_class: 'h-72', image_container_class: '', text_alignment_class: '', action_text_class: '' } %>
              <%= render partial: 'shared/card', locals: { svg_icon_path: 'plus.svg', title: 'PARTNER WITH US', description: 'Let’s join hands to make a difference in the lives of people & communities', action_text: 'START NOW', variant_class: 'h-72 mx-auto', image_container_class: '', text_alignment_class: '', action_text_class: '' } %>
              <%= render partial: 'shared/card', locals: { svg_icon_path: 'sun.svg', title: 'PRAY FOR US', description: 'Praying is a Godly principle that produces great and valued results', action_text: 'LET\'S TALK', variant_class: 'h-72 mx-auto', image_container_class: '', text_alignment_class: '', action_text_class: '' } %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        <section class=" max-w-screen-xl  mx-auto font-Outfit text-darkBlue flex flex-col justify-center align-center p-5 gap-10 ">
          <div>
            <p class="font-light text-base md:text-xxs lg:text-base lg:pb-4 mt-5 text-center">STILL HAVE QUESTIONS ABOUT US</p>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-2xl md:text-2xl  lg:text-3.8xl text-center ">LEARN MORE FROM FAQ'S</h4>
          </div>
          <div id="accordion-collapse" data-accordion="collapse">
            <!-- Accordion item 1 -->
            <h4 id="accordion-collapse-heading-1">
              <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right border border-lightGreen rounded-xl focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-200 dark:focus:ring-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 gap-3 mb-4 mt-4" data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-1">
                <span>How do I request for food?</span>
                <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-4 h-4 rotate-180 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
                  <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"/>
                </svg>
              </button>
            </h4>
            <div id="accordion-collapse-body-1" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-1">
              <div class="p-5 border border-lightGreen rounded-xl dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-900">
                <p class="mb-2">To request food from Haba Na Haba Food Bank, follow these simple steps:</p>
                <ol class="list-decimal list-inside  space-y-2">
                  <li>
                    <strong>Visit the Request Food Page:</strong> Go to the “Request Food” section on our website.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Choose Your Category:</strong> Select whether the request is for an individual, organization, or family.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Fill Out the Form:</strong> Complete the form with accurate details such as your name, contact information, and food requirements.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Submit Your Request:</strong> Click the "Submit" button to send your request. You will receive a confirmation message once your request is successfully submitted.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Wait for Approval:</strong> Our team will review your request. If approved, you will be notified via your provided contact details with further instructions.
                  </li>
                </ol>
                <p class="mt-4 ">
                  If you have any questions or face issues while submitting your request, feel free to 
                  <a href="#footer" class="text-lightGreen hover:underline">contact our support team</a>.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Accordion item 2 -->
            <h4 id="accordion-collapse-heading-2">
              <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right border border-lightGreen rounded-xl focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-200 dark:focus:ring-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 gap-3 mb-4 mt-4" data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-2">
                <span>How does a food bank operate?</span>
                <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
                  <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"/>
                </svg>
              </button>
            </h4>
            <div id="accordion-collapse-body-2" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-2">
              <div class="p-5 border border-lightGreen rounded-xl dark:border-gray-700">
                <ol class="list-decimal list-inside  space-y-4">
                  <li>
                    <strong>Food Collection:</strong> Food banks collect donations from various sources, including:
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-6">
                      <li>Individuals donating non-perishable food items.</li>
                      <li>Grocery stores and supermarkets providing surplus or unsold food.</li>
                      <li>Farms and manufacturers offering fresh produce or packaged goods.</li>
                      <li>Partnerships with local businesses, schools, and community organizations.</li>
                    </ul>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Storage and Organization:</strong> Once collected, the food is sorted and stored in warehouses to ensure it is safe and ready for distribution. Items are categorized by type, expiration date, and nutritional value.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Distribution to Partner Agencies:</strong> Food banks typically work with partner organizations, such as shelters, soup kitchens, and community groups, to distribute the food to those in need. These agencies handle direct distribution to individuals and families.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Emergency and Direct Support:</strong> Some food banks also provide direct support to individuals and families during emergencies, offering food boxes or meals.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Community Programs and Education:</strong> Food banks often run programs to educate the community about nutrition, food preparation, and reducing food waste.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Funding and Volunteer Support:</strong> Food banks rely heavily on donations, grants, and volunteers to sustain operations. Volunteers help with food sorting, packing, and distribution.
                  </li>
                </ol>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Accordion item 3 -->
            <h4 id="accordion-collapse-heading-3">
              <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right border border-lightGreen rounded-xl focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-200 dark:focus:ring-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 gap-3 mb-4 mt-4" data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-3">
                <span>Will I Recieve a reciept for my donation or contribution?</span>
                <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
                  <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"/>
                </svg>
              </button>
            </h4>
            <div id="accordion-collapse-body-3" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-3">
              <div class="p-5 border border-lightGreen rounded-xl dark:border-gray-700">
                <p class="mb-2">Yes, you will receive a receipt for your donation. For online donations, the receipt is emailed immediately after the transaction. 
                  For in-person donations, a physical receipt is provided. If you need a duplicate, contact our support team.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Accordion item 4 -->
            <h4 id="accordion-collapse-heading-4">
              <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right border border-lightGreen rounded-xl focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-200 dark:focus:ring-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 gap-3 mb-4 mt-4" data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-4">
                <span>Is HabanaHaba fook bank registered NGO?</span>
                <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
                  <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"/>
                </svg>
              </button>
            </h4>
            <div id="accordion-collapse-body-4" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-4">
              <div class="p-5 border border-lightGreen rounded-xl dark:border-gray-700">
                <p class="mb-2">Yes, Haba Na Haba Food Bank is a registered NGO in Uganda, with registration number 12122. It is recognized as a member of the Regional Food Banking Network and operates under the mentorship of the Egypt Food Bank</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        <footer id="footer" class="bg-darkBlue dark:bg-gray-900 py-5">
          <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-screen-xl p-4 py-6 lg:py-8">
            <div class="md:flex md:justify-between">
              <div class="mb-6 md:mb-0 flex-shrink-0">
